 Growth in 2025 - SpinQ](https://www.spinquanta.com/news-detail/quantum-computing-funding-explosive-growth-strategic-investment-2025)\n435\t- [Q1 2025 Quantum Investment Surge - The Quantum Insider](https://thequantuminsider.com/2025/05/27/q1-2025-quantum-technology-investment-whats-driving-the-surge-in-quantum-investment/)\n436\t- [Publicly Traded Quantum Computing Companies for 2026 - The Quantum Insider](https://thequantuminsider.com/2025/10/20/public-quantum-stocks-2025-from-pure-plays-to-tech-giants/)\n437\t- [Quantum Stock Valuations Reality Check - Motley Fool](https://www.fool.com/investing/2026/01/20/quantum-computing-stocks-415-billion-reality-check/)\n438\t- [Citi Institute: The Trillion-Dollar Security Race](https://www.citigroup.com/rcs/citigpa/storage/public/Citi_Institute_Quantum_Threat.pdf)\n439\t- [2025 Quantum Industry Report: Race to $170B by 2040](https://briandcolwell.com/2025-quantum-computing-industry-report-and-market-analysis-the-race-to-170b-by-2040/)\n440\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_018dZEMFFbxCBMwW5jUrv2aX","session_id":"fe1a4df5-a4ab-4fab-90bd-ba1de175a1ca","uuid":"c50795d5-022c-4973-877e-aa7e850ab755","timestamp":"2026-05-31T23:01:08.608Z","subagent_type":"general-purpose","task_description":"Equities & sectors research"}
