ticles/announcing-helion-fusion-ppa-with-microsoft-constellation/)\n370\t- [TAE Technologies TMTG Merger](https://www.powermag.com/trump-media-tae-merger-fusions-public-market-leap/)\n371\t\n372\t### Policy & Regulation\n373\t- [ADVANCE Act (NRC)](https://www.nrc.gov/about-nrc/governing-laws/advance-act/about-advance-act)\n374\t- [NRC Part 53 Rulemaking](https://www.nrc.gov/reactors/new-reactors/advanced/modernizing/rulemaking/part-53)\n375\t- [EO 14300 NRC Reform Actions (CATF)](https://www.catf.us/resource/actions-address-executive-order-14300-reforming-nuclear-regulatory-commission/)\n376\t- [IRA Nuclear Tax Credits (IRS)](https://www.irs.gov/credits-deductions/zero-emission-nuclear-power-production-credit)\n377\t- [DOE Loan Programs Office](https://www.energy.gov/EDF)\n378\t- [NRC Staffing Concerns (Government Executive)](https://www.govexec.com/workforce/2025/05/doge-reorganization-nuclear-regulator-prompts-concerns-about-agencys-continued-focus-safety/405712/)\n379\t\n380\t### Global Nuclear Programs\n381\t- [Nuclear Power in China (WNA)](https://world-nuclear.org/information-library/country-profiles/countries-a-f/china-nuclear-power)\n382\t- [UK Sizewell C FID (NucNet)](https://www.nucnet.org/news/uk-announces-final-investment-decision-for-gbp38-billion-sizewell-c-nuclear-power-station-7-2-2025)\n383\t- [India Nuclear Energy Mission (WNA)](https://world-nuclear.org/information-library/country-profiles/countries-g-n/india)\n384\t- [US-Saudi Nuclear Cooperation (ACA)](https://www.armscontrol.org/act/2025-12/news/us-saudi-arabia-announce-nuclear-cooperation)\n385\t\n386\t### Nuclear Waste & Storage\n387\t- [Supreme Court Clears Interim Storage (NucNet)](https://www.nucnet.org/news/us-supreme-court-paves-way-for-interim-radwaste-storage-facilities-6-4-2025)\n388\t- [Spent Fuel Recycling Steps Forward (ANS)](https://www.ans.org/news/2025-09-08/article-7348/us-nuclear-fuel-recycling-takes-two-steps-forward/)\n389\t- [EO on Reinvigorating Nuclear Industrial Base](ht