https://stockanalysis.com/stocks/smr/)\n410\t- [Oklo (OKLO) — Stock Analysis](https://stockanalysis.com/stocks/oklo/market-cap/)\n411\t- [Sprott Physical Uranium Trust](https://sprott.com/investment-strategies/exchange-listed-products/physical-commodity-funds/uranium/)\n412\t- [Global X Uranium ETF (URA)](https://www.globalxetfs.com/funds/ura)\n413\t- [Sprott Uranium Miners ETF (URNM)](https://sprottetfs.com/urnm-sprott-uranium-miners-etf)\n414\t\n415\t---\n416\t\n417\t*Research compiled February 2026. Not investment advice. Data sourced from public filings, industry reports, and news sources cited above.*\n418\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01JPmvo8LP7wReL3gw7pS53N","session_id":"fe1a4df5-a4ab-4fab-90bd-ba1de175a1ca","uuid":"4d7a3435-c880-485c-bb61-9990d823714f","timestamp":"2026-05-31T23:01:20.472Z","subagent_type":"general-purpose","task_description":"Rates, credit & Fed research"}
