{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Sk6esK77TSLziHzgozBywu","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"Bitcoin weekly recap week ending May 29 2026 BTC price level dominance\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Current price of Bitcoin for May 29, 2026 | Fortune\",\"url\":\"https://fortune.com/article/price-of-bitcoin-05-29-2026/\"},{\"title\":\"Bitcoin (BTC) Price Prediction & Forecast 2026, 2027, 2028-2030 | Binance\",\"url\":\"https://www.binance.com/en/price-prediction/bitcoin\"},{\"title\":\"Bitcoin price history May 27, 2026| Statista\",\"url\":\"https://www.statista.com/statistics/326707/bitcoin-price-index/\"},{\"title\":\"BTC Price Today: Bitcoin Holds $73.6K Amid $223M ETF Outflow\",\"url\":\"https://phemex.com/blogs/btc-price-today-may-29-2026-bitcoin-etf-outflows\"},{\"title\":\"Bitcoin and ethereum prices today, Friday, May 29, 2026: Prices open lower, despite news of U.S.-Iran truce\",\"url\":\"https://finance.yahoo.com/personal-finance/investing/article/bitcoin-and-ethereum-prices-today-friday-may-29-2026-prices-open-lower-despite-news-of-us-iran-truce-115046286.html\"},{\"title\":\"Bitcoin May 29 Price Update: Key Levels Traders Are Watching | CCDiscovery\",\"url\":\"https://www.ccdiscovery.com/btc-price-update-2026-05-29/\"},{\"title\":\"Bitcoin Price History and Historical Data | CoinMarketCap\",\"url\":\"https://coinmarketcap.com/currencies/bitcoin/historical-data/\"},{\"title\":\"Bitcoin Historical Data - Investing.com\",\"url\":\"https://www.investing.com/crypto/bitcoin/historical-data\"},{\"title\":\"Bitcoin USD (BTC-USD) Price History & Historical Data - Yahoo Finance\",\"url\":\"https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/BTC-USD/history/\"},{\"title\":\"Bitcoin Futures,May-2026 (BTC=F) Stock Historical Prices & Data - Yahoo Finance\",\"url\":\"https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/BTC=F/history/\"}]\n\nBased on the search results, here's a Bitcoin weekly recap for the week ending May 29, 2026:\n\n## Price Level\n\nAt 9:15 a.m. Eastern Time on May 29, 2026, Bitcoin was trading at $73,105.71. Bitcoin opened on Friday May 29 at $73,525.74, down 1.1% from Thursday's opening price.\n\nThroughout the week, Bitcoin was trading at $73,642.9, up a modest +1.14% over the past 24 hours but still locked inside a tightening compression range below all major moving averages.\n\n## Market Dominance\n\nRegarding market dominance, Bitcoin's market capitalization is roughly $1.33 trillion, putting it far ahead of second-place Ethereum with about $233 billion in market cap.\n\n## Additional Context\n\nBitcoin ETF outflows of $223.3M were recorded on May 28 — the single largest one-day bleed in over three weeks. Both bitcoin and ethereum opened at their lowest levels all week, with investors appearing to have less risk appetite as tensions between the U.S. and Iran grew.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01PHSkBGNFVsYNfGY6YDTHaK","session_id":"fe1a4df5-a4ab-4fab-90bd-ba1de175a1ca","uuid":"f0636e40-b5ec-4c81-bc53-a0a3023f917c","timestamp":"2026-05-31T23:01:58.047Z","subagent_type":"general-purpose","task_description":"Crypto & alternative research"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01XSuuJePYVCSPfCh5WAfkbN","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"DXY dollar index EUR/USD USD/JPY weekly May 29 2026\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"DXY — U.S. Dollar Index Chart — TradingView\",\"url\":\"https://www.tradingview.com/symbols/TVC-DXY/\"},{\"title\":\"DXY U.S. Dollar Index - Foreign Exchange Rates\",\"url\":\"https://streetstats.finance/liquidity/fx\"},{\"title\":\"United States Dollar - Quote - Chart - Historical Data - News\",\"url\":\"https://tradingeconomics.com/united-states/currency\"},{\"title\":\"US Dollar Index (DX-Y.NYB) Charts, Data & News - Yahoo Finance\",\"url\":\"https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/DX-Y.NYB/\"},{\"title\":\"US Dollar Index (DXY) Charts, Data\",\"url\":\"https://www.gurufocus.com/economic_indicators/5747/us-dollar-index-dxy\"},{\"title\":\"DXY Index Explained: US Dollar Index Guide 2026 | Financer\",\"url\":\"https://financer.com/invest/dxy-index/\"},{\"title\":\"DOLLAR INDEX (DXY) FORECAST 2026, 2027, 2028 - 2030 - Long Forecast\",\"url\":\"https://longforecast.com/dollar-index\"},{\"title\":\"US Dollar Index (DXY) Today | DealPlexus\",\"url\":\"https://www.dealplexus.com/markets/usd-index-dxy\"},{\"title\":\"DXY Dollar Index - Currency Exchange Rate Live Price Chart\",\"url\":\"https://tradingeconomics.com/dxy:cur\"},{\"title\":\"DXY Forecast Tracker 2026: Live Dollar Consensus Divergence | AhaSignals\",\"url\":\"https://ahasignals.com/dxy-forecast-tracker/\"}]\n\nBased on the web search results, here's what I found about the DXY Dollar Index, EUR/USD, and USD/JPY for the week ending May 29, 2026:\n\n## DXY Dollar Index (as of May 29, 2026)\n\nThe dollar index was little changed at 99 on Friday, close to two-week lows, but was on track to end the May month about 1% higher.\n\nThe dollar index hovered around 99 on Friday after weakening in the previous session, as reports that the US and Iran had reached a tentative peace agreement eased concerns over inflation and future interest rate hikes.\n\n## Market Context for the Week\n\nThe latest US PCE price index data showed softer-than-expected inflation readings, helping calm fears that the recent energy shock would significantly worsen the inflation outlook. This softer inflation data contributed to pressure on the dollar during the week.\n\n## Index Composition\n\nThe EUR is, by far, the largest component of the index, making up 57.6% of the basket followed by JPY (13.6%), GBP (11.9%), CAD (9.1%), SEK (4.2%), and CHF (3.6%).\n\nThe DXY's heavy weighting toward EUR/USD means that movements in that pair have the most significant impact on the dollar index during the week.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01Q8Kwt517HqYVMRhJgQ1kZ1","session_id":"fe1a4df5-a4ab-4fab-90bd-ba1de175a1ca","uuid":"03973224-152f-481e-8dad-0775ae5eb475","timestamp":"2026-05-31T23:01:58.069Z","subagent_type":"general-purpose","task_description":"Commodities & forex research"}
