{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Kf32STKCMcA4r8NMhYgKWF","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"uranium spot price May 2026 U3O8 weekly\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Uranium - Price - Chart - Historical Data - News\",\"url\":\"https://tradingeconomics.com/commodity/uranium\"},{\"title\":\"Daily Uranium Spot Price Indicator\",\"url\":\"https://www.uranium.info/daily_U3O8_spot_price_indicator.php\"},{\"title\":\"UxC Uranium U3O8 Quotes - CME Group\",\"url\":\"https://www.cmegroup.com/markets/metals/other/uranium.html\"},{\"title\":\"TradeTech – Uranium Prices & Analysis since 1968\",\"url\":\"https://www.uranium.info/\"},{\"title\":\"UxC: Nuclear Fuel Price Indicators\",\"url\":\"https://www.uxc.com/p/price\"},{\"title\":\"Uranium spot pricing oracle | U3O8 | Powered by Tezos\",\"url\":\"https://price.uranium.io/en\"},{\"title\":\"Uranium Spot Price (Monthly) - Historical Data & Trends\",\"url\":\"https://ycharts.com/indicators/uranium_spot_price\"},{\"title\":\"Current Uranium Price Per Lb U3O8 & Per Ton Farmonaut®\",\"url\":\"https://farmonaut.com/mining/current-uranium-price-per-lb-u3o8-per-ton-2026\"},{\"title\":\"Global price of Uranium (PURANUSDM) | FRED | St. Louis Fed\",\"url\":\"https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/PURANUSDM\"},{\"title\":\"Sprott Physical Uranium Trust | Sprott\",\"url\":\"https://sprott.com/investment-strategies/exchange-listed-products/physical-commodity-funds/uranium/\"}]\n\nBased on the search results for uranium spot prices in May 2026, here's what I found:\n\n## Uranium Spot Price (U3O8) - May 2026\n\nUranium futures in the US were above $86.5 per pound as of late May 2026, near their highest level in two months. More specifically, uranium futures eased to below $85 per pound in late May, the lowest in nearly two months.\n\n### Market Context\n\nThe cooldown of the speculative rally at the start of the year drove the market's focus back to muted levels of spot buying by utilities, which have already been largely reliant on long-term contracts.\n\nThe market has been supported by several factors, including geopolitical tension driving power markets in major economies to be increasingly volatile, sparking interest in nuclear power by governments and power-hungry AI hyperscalers that develop datacenters.\n\n**Note:** The search results provide general price ranges for May 2026 but don't contain specific weekly data points. For detailed weekly spot price indicators, you would need to access specialized uranium pricing services like TradeTech or UxC, which may require paid subscriptions for detailed historical weekly data.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01Q8Kwt517HqYVMRhJgQ1kZ1","session_id":"fe1a4df5-a4ab-4fab-90bd-ba1de175a1ca","uuid":"d502d112-12a7-4a95-8ed6-0690ce16b005","timestamp":"2026-05-31T23:02:08.125Z","subagent_type":"general-purpose","task_description":"Commodities & forex research"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01KtBsduBVMt9uJUBFr2fB1t","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"natural gas price Henry Hub May 29 2026 EIA storage\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Short-Term Energy Outlook: Natural Gas\",\"url\":\"https://www.eia.gov/outlooks/steo/report/natgas.php\"},{\"title\":\"Henry Hub Natural Gas Spot Price (Dollars per Million Btu)\",\"url\":\"https://www.eia.gov/dnav/ng/hist/rngwhhdm.htm\"},{\"title\":\"Henry Hub Natural Gas Spot Price (DHHNGSP) | FRED | St. Louis Fed\",\"url\":\"https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/DHHNGSP\"},{\"title\":\"Natural Gas Weekly Update\",\"url\":\"https://www.eia.gov/naturalgas/weekly/\"},{\"title\":\"We expect Henry Hub natural gas spot prices to fall slightly in 2026 before rising in 2027 - U.S. Energy Information Administration (EIA)\",\"url\":\"https://www.eia.gov/todayinenergy/detail.php?id=67004\"},{\"title\":\"Natural gas - Price - Chart - Historical Data - News\",\"url\":\"https://tradingeconomics.com/commodity/natural-gas\"},{\"title\":\"Henry Hub Natural Gas Spot Price (Market Daily) - United St…\",\"url\":\"https://ycharts.com/indicators/henry_hub_natural_gas_spot_price\"},{\"title\":\"Natural Gas Data - U.S. Energy Information Administration (EIA)\",\"url\":\"https://www.eia.gov/naturalgas/data.php\"},{\"title\":\"May 2026 Short-Term Energy Outlook\",\"url\":\"https://www.eia.gov/outlooks/steo/pdf/steo_full.pdf\"},{\"title\":\"EIA Sees Henry Hub Natural Gas Prices Strengthening Substantially Amid Winter’s Bullish Grip\",\"url\":\"https://naturalgasintel.com/news/eia-sees-henry-hub-natural-gas-prices-strengthening-substantially-amid-winters-bullish-grip/\"}]\n\nBased on the search results, here's what I found regarding natural gas prices, Henry Hub, and EIA storage data for late May 2026:\n\n## Henry Hub Natural Gas Prices\n\nAs of May 28, 2026, natural gas increased to 3.21 USD/MMBtu, the highest since March 2026. For the specific date you mentioned, while I don't have the exact May 29, 2026 price in the results, the most recent data from May 28 shows prices at $3.21/MMBtu.\n\n## EIA Storage Data\n\nThe EIA reported that utilities added 92 billion cubic feet of gas to storage in the week ended May 22, below forecasts for a 95 to 96 bcf increase and lower than the 104 bcf injection recorded a year earlier. Total inventories rose to 2.483 trillion cubic feet, around 0.9% above year-ago levels and 6.2% higher than the five-year seasonal average.\n\n## 2026 Outlook\n\nThe EIA expects the Henry Hub price to average about $3.50/MMBtu in 2026. Additionally, the EIA forecasts U.S. natural gas inventories will end the injection season on October 31 at 7% above the previous five-year average.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01Q8Kwt517HqYVMRhJgQ1kZ1","session_id":"fe1a4df5-a4ab-4fab-90bd-ba1de175a1ca","uuid":"fe3db021-3b8e-469d-82c3-6bad15bed5c5","timestamp":"2026-05-31T23:02:09.016Z","subagent_type":"general-purpose","task_description":"Commodities & forex research"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01JTcRWUhfzdDXshyxHikAZA","type":"tool_result","content":"# Bitcoin Market Report: May 29, 2026\n\n## Current Price & 24-Hour Performance\nBitcoin traded at **$73,642.90** on Phemex BTC/USDT Perpetual, up **+1.14% ($833.10)** over the preceding 24 hours.\n\n## ETF Outflow Data\nThe most significant metric was spot Bitcoin ETF outflows: **-$223.30 million** recorded on May 28, marking \"the largest single-day bleed in over three weeks.\" Monthly trends showed cumulative outflows of -$89.70 million, while three-month net flows stood at -$26.64 million. Total ETF assets under management reached approximately **$106 billion**.\n\n## Technical Levels & Price Range\n- **24-hour high**: $73,922.10\n- **24-hour low**: $72,561.70\n- **Daily volatility**: 0.99% (compressed range)\n- **Key resistance**: $75,513.20 (7-day moving average)\n- **Critical support**: $62,872 (52-week close low)\n\n## Market Context\nThe analysis noted that \"Bitcoin is trading...still locked inside a tightening compression range below all major moving averages,\" with momentum indicators (MFI at 27.93) signaling oversold conditions not seen in approximately four months."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01PHSkBGNFVsYNfGY6YDTHaK","session_id":"fe1a4df5-a4ab-4fab-90bd-ba1de175a1ca","uuid":"d0d351a0-1fe9-4609-b17c-b46ac4099473","timestamp":"2026-05-31T23:02:10.844Z","subagent_type":"general-purpose","task_description":"Crypto & alternative research"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_016z56sZn28GBVs3cQKSFcef","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"Iran Strait of Hormuz oil news May 30 31 2026 weekend Trump deal\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"May 29-30, 2026 — US military ready to resume combat in Gulf if needed, defense secretary warns | CNN\",\"url\":\"https://www.cnn.com/2026/05/29/world/live-news/iran-trump-war-news\"},{\"title\":\"Live Updates: Trump recently edited possible U.S.-Iran agreement, including on enriched uranium and Strait of Hormuz, source says\",\"url\":\"https://www.cbsnews.com/live-updates/iran-war-us-trump-vance-ceasefire-strait-of-hormuz-deal-close/\"},{\"title\":\"Oil prices: U.S. strikes in Iran revive fear over Strait of Hormuz\",\"url\":\"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/05/28/oil-prices-us-strikes-in-iran-revive-strait-of-hormuz-turmoil-fears.html\"},{\"title\":\"U.S. military strikes Iran as Trump says negotiations move forward for deal to end war\",\"url\":\"https://www.npr.org/2026/05/25/nx-s1-5833690/u-s-iran-negotiations-updates\"},{\"title\":\"Trump sent back Iran deal text with changes | CNN Politics\",\"url\":\"https://www.cnn.com/2026/05/31/politics/trump-iran-deal-changes\"},{\"title\":\"Live Updates: Hegseth signals US military is ready after Trump Situation Room meeting ends without deal | Fox News Digital\",\"url\":\"https://www.foxnews.com/live-news/iran-war-news-trump-update-strait-hormuz-lebanon-oil-prices-may-30.amp\"}]\n\nBased on the latest news from May 30-31, 2026, here's what's happening with Iran, the Strait of Hormuz, and potential oil-related deal negotiations:\n\n## Deal Status\n\nIran and the United States reached a tentative agreement to turn the existing ceasefire into a more long-lasting settlement, US officials said Thursday. However, President Donald Trump sent back changes to the proposed deal with Iran after a meeting with advisers Friday, officials said, extending the back-and-forth negotiations into another week.\n\n## Trump's Key Demands\n\nOn Friday, President Donald Trump made a series of demands — on the Strait of Hormuz, Iran's nuclear program and the unfreezing of Iranian assets held overseas - that did not go down well in Tehran. Specifically, Trump has pushed for tougher language on Iran's nuclear commitments and the reopening of the Strait of Hormuz.\n\n## Oil Market Impact\n\nFor the last three months, the Strait of Hormuz — which normally carries one-fifth of the world's oil — has been closed to most shipping traffic. The leaders of three international economic organizations warned Friday that if oil shipping doesn't return to normal, there could be \"increasing risks for fuel security, market conditions, and broader economic resilience\" when demand picks up this summer.\n\n## Iran's Response\n\nAn adviser to Iran's Supreme Leader said on Saturday, \"By continuing the naval blockade and making excessive demands in negotiations, he has once again proven that he is not inclined toward negotiation and is pursuing other objectives.\"\n\nThe negotiations remain ongoing with both sides working toward an agreement, though key sticking points remain unresolved.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01Q8Kwt517HqYVMRhJgQ1kZ1","session_id":"fe1a4df5-a4ab-4fab-90bd-ba1de175a1ca","uuid":"dcb80e9b-d169-40f0-bd97-1d8e0ac7c203","timestamp":"2026-05-31T23:02:10.971Z","subagent_type":"general-purpose","task_description":"Commodities & forex research"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01SMd53XT16QL3rPr5cyHXZV","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"Bitcoin ETF flows week May 25 29 2026 IBIT FBTC net outflows\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Bitcoin ETF Fund Flows | Spot BTC Net Inflow & Holdings | CoinGlass\",\"url\":\"https://www.coinglass.com/etf/bitcoin\"},{\"title\":\"Bitcoin ETF Flow (US$m) – Farside Investors\",\"url\":\"https://farside.co.uk/btc/\"},{\"title\":\"Bitcoin ETF Flows [Table & Chart]\",\"url\":\"https://bitbo.io/treasuries/etf-flows/\"},{\"title\":\"Bitcoin ETF Flows May 2026: 6-Day Outflow Streak\",\"url\":\"https://bitcoinfoundation.org/news/crypto-etfs-news/crypto-etf-may/\"},{\"title\":\"Spot Bitcoin ETF Flows Daily Chart: BlackRock, Fidelity and More\",\"url\":\"https://www.theblock.co/data/etfs/bitcoin-etf/spot-bitcoin-etf-flows\"},{\"title\":\"Bitcoin ETF List Data\",\"url\":\"https://coinmarketcap.com/etf/bitcoin/\"},{\"title\":\"Bitcoin US Spot ETF Net Flows Chart - Glassnode\",\"url\":\"https://studio.glassnode.com/charts/institutions.UsSpotEtfFlowsNet?a=BTC\"},{\"title\":\"Bitcoin ETFs Post Ninth Straight Day of Outflows as IBIT Notches Near-Record Redemption\",\"url\":\"https://www.blockhead.co/2026/05/29/bitcoin-etfs-post-ninth-straight-day-of-outflows-as-ibit-notches-near-record-redemption/\"},{\"title\":\"Bitcoin ETF Flows 2026: Institutional Investors Retreat After ...\",\"url\":\"https://intellectia.ai/blog/bitcoin-etf-flows-2026-analysis\"},{\"title\":\"Bitcoin ETF Flows Today - Daily Inflows & Outflows Tracker | CryptoSignalApp\",\"url\":\"https://cryptosignalapp.com/etf/flows\"}]\n\nBased on the search results, here's what happened with Bitcoin ETF flows during the week of May 25-29, 2026:\n\n## Net Outflows Week of May 25-29, 2026\n\nTotal outflows over six days reached $1.55B, representing a significant period of redemptions in the Bitcoin ETF space.\n\n### IBIT (BlackRock)\nThe outflow leader for the week was BlackRock's IBIT at $68.9M on Friday. However, the situation was much more severe earlier in the week. On Wednesday (May 27), the 11 U.S.-listed spot bitcoin ETFs lost a combined $733.43 million, with BlackRock's IBIT accounting for $527.84 million — the fund's second-largest single-day net outflow on record. Additionally, U.S. spot bitcoin ETFs recorded their ninth consecutive session of net outflows on Thursday (May 29), with BlackRock's iShares Bitcoin Trust (IBIT) leading with outflows of $177.94 million.\n\n### FBTC (Fidelity)\nFidelity's FBTC also saw significant losses at $36.3M on Friday. Fidelity's FBTC lost $60.30 million on Wednesday (May 27).\n\n### Context\nNet inflows into bitcoin ETFs since the start of 2026 have shrunk to $536M as a result of these sustained outflows.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01PHSkBGNFVsYNfGY6YDTHaK","session_id":"fe1a4df5-a4ab-4fab-90bd-ba1de175a1ca","uuid":"d1fab972-82fa-493c-ae3a-cc6b2ba780ab","timestamp":"2026-05-31T23:02:11.459Z","subagent_type":"general-purpose","task_description":"Crypto & alternative research"}
