{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_018dGpMX2Vci7hLWa9vT6hUt","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"CrowdStrike Zscaler earnings late May 2026 cybersecurity stock reaction\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Cybersecurity stocks are surging. One looks promising into earnings\",\"url\":\"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/05/26/cybersecurity-stocks-are-surging-one-looks-promising-into-earnings.html\"},{\"title\":\"Our cyber stocks are falling on a rival's earnings blowup. Why it's not a cause for concern\",\"url\":\"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/05/27/our-cyber-stocks-are-falling-on-a-rivals-earnings-blowup-why-its-not-a-cause-for-concern.html\"},{\"title\":\"AI Is Reshaping Cybersecurity Threats: Why Zscaler and CrowdStrike Could Be Long-Term Winners | The Motley Fool\",\"url\":\"https://www.fool.com/investing/2026/05/05/ai-is-reshaping-cybersecurity-threats-why-zscaler/\"},{\"title\":\"CrowdStrike Holdings, Inc. (CRWD) Stock Price, News, Quote & History - Yahoo Finance\",\"url\":\"https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/CRWD/\"},{\"title\":\"Q4 Cybersecurity Earnings: CrowdStrike (NASDAQ:CRWD) Earns Top Marks - StockStory\",\"url\":\"https://stockstory.org/us/stocks/nasdaq/crwd/news/earnings/q4-cybersecurity-earnings-crowdstrike-nasdaqcrwd-earns-top-marks\"},{\"title\":\"Best Cybersecurity Stocks to Buy in 2026: Defensive Play or Overcrowded Trade? | TECHi\",\"url\":\"https://www.techi.com/best-cybersecurity-stocks/\"},{\"title\":\"Zscaler Q1 Earnings Today: Options Traders Brace for Massive 13% Post-Report Swing - TipRanks.com\",\"url\":\"https://www.tipranks.com/news/zscaler-is-about-to-report-q3-earnings-tomorrow-options-traders-expect-a-13-move-in-zs-stock\"},{\"title\":\"ZScaler earnings cause security stocks to tumble, Wiz puts data to supply chain risk, and the Megalodon strikes\",\"url\":\"https://www.cybersecuritypulse.net/p/zscaler-earnings-cause-security-stocks\"},{\"title\":\"Earnings call transcript: CrowdStrike beats Q3 2026 forecasts, stock rises By Investing.com\",\"url\":\"https://www.investing.com/news/transcripts/earnings-call-transcript-crowdstrike-beats-q3-2026-forecasts-stock-rises-93CH-4387248\"}]\n\nBased on the search results, here's what happened with cybersecurity stocks in late May 2026:\n\n## Zscaler Earnings Miss and Stock Reaction\n\nZscaler reported a strong Q3 with revenue up 25% YoY to $850.5M and ARR up 25% YoY to $3.525B, but the stock still sold off after softer forward guidance. The company guided for sales below expectations for the current quarter and into the next fiscal year, where it expects revenue to grow 16% to 17% versus the 19.5% FactSet consensus. The result is a stock down 30% on Wednesday morning.\n\n## Impact on CrowdStrike and Palo Alto Networks\n\nPalo Alto Networks and CrowdStrike on Wednesday are falling in reaction to cybersecurity peer ZScaler's earnings debacle the prior evening. Shares of Palo Alto and CrowdStrike are down almost 4% and 3%, respectively, on Wednesday.\n\nHowever, analysts pushed back on the broader implications. Wedbush analyst Dan Ives came out in defense of Palo Alto and CrowdStrike, raising his price targets to $300 and $700, respectively, arguing the poor guidance from ZScaler is the result of \"company specific execution issues and not an indicator of broader sector issues.\"\n\nZScaler's problems may well be the result of those two [Palo Alto and CrowdStrike] winning all the business as the historically fragmented cybersecurity industry trends toward vendor consolidation.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_018dZEMFFbxCBMwW5jUrv2aX","session_id":"fe1a4df5-a4ab-4fab-90bd-ba1de175a1ca","uuid":"d9634906-bb14-43e7-8f55-0b97cd1c4001","timestamp":"2026-05-31T23:02:14.386Z","subagent_type":"general-purpose","task_description":"Equities & sectors research"}
