{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01AUpYevfT3whg7C26re2ZK3","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"Dell Snowflake earnings May 2026 stock reaction beat guidance Nvidia week\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"DELL Stock in 2026: Soars to $317, Jumps 39% on AI Server Boom\",\"url\":\"https://phemex.com/academy/dell-stock-2026-ai-server-growth\"},{\"title\":\"Palantir Soars 10% as Dell Earnings Beat Validates Their AI Factory Partnership, Snowflake Lifts Software Rally - 24/7 Wall St.\",\"url\":\"https://247wallst.com/investing/2026/05/29/palantir-soars-9-as-dell-earnings-beat-validates-their-ai-factory-partnership-snowflake-lifts-software-rally/\"},{\"title\":\"DELL Stock Soars As AI Server Boom Resets Wall Street Expectations - StocksToTrade\",\"url\":\"https://stockstotrade.com/news/dell-technologies-inc-class-c-dell-news-2026_05_29/\"},{\"title\":\"Dell Stock Soars to Record High After Crushing Earnings, Here’s Why the AI Boom Is Just Getting Started | by Earl Cotten | Newsarticulated | May, 2026 | Medium\",\"url\":\"https://medium.com/newsarticulated/dell-stock-soars-to-record-high-after-crushing-earnings-heres-why-the-ai-boom-is-just-getting-8d050f3b6660\"},{\"title\":\"Dell Technologies Inc (DELL) Stock Price & News - Google Finance\",\"url\":\"https://www.google.com/finance/beta/quote/DELL:NYSE\"},{\"title\":\"Dell stock skyrockets 32% for its best day ever as AI server revenue soars\",\"url\":\"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/05/29/dell-stock-earnings-ai-servers.html\"},{\"title\":\"Dell stock surges after beating Q1 estimates & guidance hike By Investing.com\",\"url\":\"https://www.investing.com/news/earnings/dell-soars-after-hours-on-blowout-results-raised-full-year-revenue-guidance-4715307\"},{\"title\":\"Dell Technologies (DELL) Stock Price & Overview\",\"url\":\"https://stockanalysis.com/stocks/dell/\"},{\"title\":\"Snowflake Inc. - Form 8-K - FY2026\",\"url\":\"https://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/0001640147/000164014726000027/fy2027q1earnings.htm\"}]\n\nBased on the search results, here's what happened with Dell and Snowflake earnings in May 2026:\n\n## Dell Earnings Beat and Stock Reaction\n\nDell reported a blowout Q1 with adjusted EPS of $4.86 versus $2.96 consensus and revenue of $43.8B versus $35.77B, powered by $24.4B in AI orders and $16.1B in AI server revenue. Quarterly revenue soared nearly 88% year over year, with AI server revenue alone increasing 757% from a year earlier to $16.1 billion.\n\nThe stock reaction was dramatic: $317.05 close, $441.00 after-hours (+39.09%) on May 29, 2026. Shares are now up 234% in 2026.\n\nThe surge was almost certainly an earnings beat plus raised guidance tied to the AI server supercycle (PowerEdge XE-series, hyperscaler + enterprise demand). Management substantially raised its FY27 outlook, boosting adjusted EPS guidance to $17.90 at the midpoint from $12.90 and lifting the FY27 revenue target to $165B–$169B.\n\n## Snowflake Earnings\n\nSnowflake reported Q1 FY27 revenue of $1.39 billion, up 34% YoY, with non-GAAP EPS of $0.39 beating by 22%. The company raised its full-year product revenue guidance to $5.84 billion, a 31% growth pace, and disclosed more than 13,600 accounts using its AI capabilities. Snowflake reported Q1 revenue of $1.39B, up 34% YoY with 13,600+ accounts using its AI capabilities, sparking a broader software rally.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_018dZEMFFbxCBMwW5jUrv2aX","session_id":"fe1a4df5-a4ab-4fab-90bd-ba1de175a1ca","uuid":"9dcc45e4-c062-4c4d-8003-016cfdac0689","timestamp":"2026-05-31T23:02:15.235Z","subagent_type":"general-purpose","task_description":"Equities & sectors research"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01KFPnT8Ct2mh7irEVnzyMr1","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"Nvidia stock May 2026 week AI semiconductors Broadcom Palantir performance\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Top 5 AI Stocks for May 2026: Nvidia (NVDA), AMD, Broadcom Lead Investor Watchlist - Blockonomi\",\"url\":\"https://blockonomi.com/top-5-ai-stocks-for-may-2026-nvidia-nvda-amd-broadcom-lead-investor-watchlist/\"},{\"title\":\"Palantir Just Showed Why Nvidia Stock Can Plunge on May 21 | The Motley Fool\",\"url\":\"https://www.fool.com/investing/2026/05/11/palantir-show-why-nvidia-stock-can-plunge-may-21/\"},{\"title\":\"Top 5 AI Stocks for May 2026: Nvidia (NVDA), AMD, Broadcom Lead Investor Watchlist | MEXC News\",\"url\":\"https://www.mexc.com/news/1070030\"},{\"title\":\"3 AI Stocks That Will Trounce Palantir in 2026, According to Wall Street\",\"url\":\"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/3-ai-stocks-trounce-palantir-100400493.html\"},{\"title\":\"Nvidia, Palantir, and Broadcom Are Sending Shockwaves Through Wall Street With This $4.6 Billion Warning | The Motley Fool\",\"url\":\"https://www.fool.com/investing/2026/05/04/nvda-pltr-avgo-send-wall-street-46-billion-warning/\"},{\"title\":\"Top 5 AI Stocks for May 2026: Nvidia (NVDA), AMD, Broadcom Lead the Pack - Parameter\",\"url\":\"https://parameter.io/top-5-ai-stocks-for-may-2026-nvidia-nvda-amd-broadcom-lead-the-pack/\"},{\"title\":\"Best AI Stocks To Watch In May 2026: Nvidia, AMD and Broadcom Top the List - CoinCentral\",\"url\":\"https://coincentral.com/best-ai-stocks-to-watch-in-may-2026-nvidia-amd-and-broadcom-top-the-list/\"},{\"title\":\"Meet the AI Stock Crushing Palantir, Nvidia, and Alphabet Right Now | The Motley Fool\",\"url\":\"https://www.fool.com/investing/2026/05/13/meet-the-ai-stock-crushing-palantir-nvidia-and-alp/\"},{\"title\":\"Nvidia vs. Palantir: The Better AI Stock to Own in 2026 | The Motley Fool\",\"url\":\"https://www.fool.com/investing/2026/05/07/nvidia-vs-palantir-the-better-ai-stock-to-own-2026/\"},{\"title\":\"Nvidia vs. Palantir Stock Analysis: AI Hardware vs. Software in 2026 - News and Statistics - IndexBox\",\"url\":\"https://www.indexbox.io/blog/nvidia-vs-palantir-ai-stock-analysis-shows-valuation-gap-and-market-focus/\"}]\n\nBased on the search results, here's what's happening with these AI semiconductor and software stocks in May 2026:\n\n## Nvidia Stock Performance\n\nNvidia continues its dominance in AI semiconductors, with data-center momentum and forward guidance under investor scrutiny. However, the stock's May performance has been mixed. Nvidia is up 18% year to date, though Nvidia stock has struggled over the last week according to reports from May 27, 2026.\n\n## Broadcom's Position\n\nBroadcom specializes in bespoke AI processors, networking components, and cloud backbone technology. As technology titans develop proprietary AI architectures, Broadcom captures demand for application-specific integrated circuits. Broadcom has been one of the best-performing AI stocks not named Palantir over the last 12 months. Demand for its AI semiconductors has been robust, helping drive the company's overall revenue 28% higher year over year in the fourth quarter of 2025.\n\n## Palantir's Performance\n\nPalantir crushed expectations with its first-quarter operating results. Revenue soared 85% to $1.63 billion on the heels of 84% growth in U.S. government revenue and a more-than-doubling in U.S. commercial sales. CEO Alex Karp also upped Palantir's 2026 full-year sales guidance from 61% sales growth to a new projection of 71%. Despite strong fundamentals, Palantir is down 24% year to date.\n\n## Overall Market Context\n\nToday's investors require tangible evidence — confirmed revenue streams, expanding profit margins, and financial results proving that AI capital expenditures deliver returns, with valuations remaining a key concern across these stocks.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_018dZEMFFbxCBMwW5jUrv2aX","session_id":"fe1a4df5-a4ab-4fab-90bd-ba1de175a1ca","uuid":"49bc8b8a-89a6-4cd4-a19c-00bda77641f0","timestamp":"2026-05-31T23:02:15.280Z","subagent_type":"general-purpose","task_description":"Equities & sectors research"}
