{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_0136GvMeG3YnYHbj2RVPvZiW","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"lithium carbonate price rare earth May 2026 China export\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Lithium - Price - Chart - Historical Data - News\",\"url\":\"https://tradingeconomics.com/commodity/lithium\"},{\"title\":\"Lithium carbonate prices - daily spot, price charts, full history\",\"url\":\"https://www.fastmarkets.com/metals-and-mining/battery-raw-materials/lithium/lithium-carbonate-prices/\"},{\"title\":\"China Lithium carbonate spot price, China Lithium carbonate Daily prices provided by SunSirs, China Commodity Data Group\",\"url\":\"https://www.sunsirs.com/m/page/commodity-price-detail/commodity-price-detail-1162.html\"},{\"title\":\"Battery-Grade Lithium Carbonate, Price of Lithium Per Ton Today, Lithium Prices Charts - Shanghai Metals Market (SMM)\",\"url\":\"https://www.metal.com/Chemical-Compound/201102250059\"},{\"title\":\"Lithium Prices Chart, Lithium Metal Price Today, Lithium Carbonate Price, Lithium Hydroxide Price - Shanghai Metals Market (SMM)\",\"url\":\"https://www.metal.com/Lithium\"},{\"title\":\"Lithium Prices Surge Amid Strong Demand Forecasts, Could Reach Up to $28,000/Ton by 2026\",\"url\":\"https://carboncredits.com/lithium-prices-surge-amid-strong-demand-forecasts-could-reach-up-to-28000-ton-by-2026-nili/\"},{\"title\":\"Lithium Carbonate 99%Min China Spot Historical Prices - Investing.com\",\"url\":\"https://www.investing.com/commodities/lithium-carbonate-99-min-china-futures-historical-data\"},{\"title\":\"Lithium Carbonate Price Index, Chart 2026 & Forecast\",\"url\":\"https://www.imarcgroup.com/lithium-carbonate-pricing-report\"},{\"title\":\"Lithium prices, news and research - Asian Metal\",\"url\":\"https://www.asianmetal.com/LithiumPrice/Lithium.html\"},{\"title\":\"Lithium Carbonate Price Trends, Chart And Forecast 2026\",\"url\":\"https://www.price-watch.ai/lithium-carbonate-prices/\"}]\n\nI've found detailed information about lithium carbonate prices in China as of May 2026. Here are the key findings:\n\n## Lithium Carbonate Prices in China (May 2026)\n\nLithium carbonate prices in China were at CNY 191,000 per tonne as of May 20, 2026, easing from the over two-year high of CNY 200,500 from May 13th as the surge in prices drove producers to restart mining activity.\n\n## Market Dynamics\n\nLithium carbonate prices in China rose past $195,000 per tonne in May, the highest in nearly three years, amid evidence of strong demand and supply tightness.\n\n## Demand Factors in China\n\nNew data in top consumer China showed that new energy vehicles output, the top source of lithium demand due to their batteries, rose by 5.5% annually to 1.32 million units, while sales rose by 9.7% to 1.34 million units. Demand also remained supported by Chinese investment in power infrastructure, with Beijing stating it would double national EV charging capacity to 180 gigawatts by 2027.\n\n## Export-Related Developments\n\nRegarding exports, Zimbabwe imposed export quotas for lithium concentrates and a full export ban to start next year, and stated exports would be allowed for processed lithium to stimulate the investment in local processing.\n\nNote: Your search query included \"rare earth,\" but the results focused on lithium rather than rare earth minerals, as lithium carbonate was the primary topic available in the search results for May 2026.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01Q8Kwt517HqYVMRhJgQ1kZ1","session_id":"fe1a4df5-a4ab-4fab-90bd-ba1de175a1ca","uuid":"fdf74cf8-1282-4215-afbb-bd63a3e646d5","timestamp":"2026-05-31T23:02:23.336Z","subagent_type":"general-purpose","task_description":"Commodities & forex research"}
