{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Jk6LV2uepUe6aWN4E4ovd6","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"quantum computing stocks IonQ Rigetti D-Wave May 2026 week rally\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Quantum Computing Stocks IonQ, Rigetti Computing, and D-Wave Quantum Are Sending Shockwaves Through Wall Street With This $931 Million Warning | The Motley Fool\",\"url\":\"https://www.fool.com/investing/2026/05/28/quantum-computing-ionq-rgti-qbts-wall-st-warning/\"},{\"title\":\"Quantum Computing Stocks IonQ, Rigetti, and D-Wave Have Soared Up to 72% in 7 Trading Sessions -- and You'll Likely Regret Chasing This Rally | The Motley Fool\",\"url\":\"https://www.fool.com/investing/2026/04/24/quantum-computing-stocks-ionq-rgti-qbts-soar-72/\"},{\"title\":\"Quantum stocks soar as U.S. plans $2 billion funding incentives and equity stakes\",\"url\":\"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/05/21/quantum-stocks--us-taking-equity-stakes.html\"},{\"title\":\"Quantum computing stocks are rising again: How long will the rally last for QUBT, D-Wave, IonQ, and Rigetti?\",\"url\":\"https://www.fastcompany.com/91540645/quantum-computing-stocks-why-d-wave-ionq-rigetti-rising-rally-last\"},{\"title\":\"Which Quantum Computing Stock Has Dominated in 2026: IonQ, Rigetti, or D-Wave? - 24/7 Wall St.\",\"url\":\"https://247wallst.com/investing/2026/05/06/which-quantum-computing-stock-has-dominated-in-2026-ionq-rigetti-or-d-wave/\"},{\"title\":\"Which Quantum Computing Stock Has Dominated in 2026: IonQ, Rigetti, or D-Wave? - AOL\",\"url\":\"https://www.aol.com/articles/quantum-computing-stock-dominated-2026-192959784.html\"},{\"title\":\"Quantum computing stocks are rising again: How long will the rally last for QUBT, D-Wave, IonQ, and Rigetti?\",\"url\":\"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/quantum-computing-stocks-rising-again-121100359.html\"},{\"title\":\"Quantum Computing Stocks IonQ and D-Wave Quantum Have Nearly Doubled in 5 Weeks -- Don't Take the Bait | The Motley Fool\",\"url\":\"https://www.fool.com/investing/2026/05/12/quantum-computing-stocks-ionq-qbts-have-doubled/\"},{\"title\":\"Quantum Computing Stocks 2026: IonQ, Rigetti, D-Wave Guide\",\"url\":\"https://www.heygotrade.com/en/blog/quantum-computing-stocks-2026/\"},{\"title\":\"How Your Quantum Stock Faves Perform After Major Bull Gaps - Schaeffer's Investment Research\",\"url\":\"https://www.schaeffersresearch.com/content/bgs/2026/05/26/how-your-quantum-stock-faves-perform-after-major-bull-gaps\"}]\n\nBased on the search results, here's what's been happening with quantum computing stocks IonQ, Rigetti, and D-Wave in May 2026:\n\n## May 2026 Rally Overview\n\nA rally in quantum computing stocks kicked off about a month ago around World Quantum Day, with D-Wave Quantum Inc., IonQ Inc., Quantum Computing Inc., and Rigetti Computing recovering much of their 2026 losses.\n\n## Recent Weekly Performance\n\nIonQ stock blasted almost 23% higher the week of May 22. More dramatically, QBTS (D-Wave), IONQ (IonQ), and RGTI (Rigetti) settled Thursday with impressive session gains of 33.4%, 12.2%, and 30.1% respectively following government funding announcements.\n\n## Key Catalyst: Government Funding\n\nShares of D-Wave added 33%, Rigetti soared 30% and other quantum firms climbed on the news, with IonQ popping 12% due to a U.S. government funding initiative. D-Wave and Rigetti have already penned letters of intent to secure $100 million in funding under CHIPS.\n\n## Year-to-Date Performance\n\nAs of mid-October 2025, trailing 12-month returns for IonQ, Rigetti Computing, and D-Wave Quantum were up to 6,217%. However, performance varies significantly in 2026, with IonQ trading at around $5250 intraday on May 6, up 9% on the day, with shares up 16% year to date, the only positive return among the three pure-play quantum names.\n\n## Valuation Concerns\n\nAs of May 22, IonQ, Rigetti, and D-Wave are trading at P/S ratios of 109, 836, and 791, respectively.\n\n\nREMI