{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_011QTweoYw1S5WBnr8YfNRYL","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"Trump Xi summit May 2026 rare earth trade deal China agreement date\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Trump-Xi Summit: China's Rare-Earth Trade Leverage Looms Over Talks\",\"url\":\"https://foreignpolicy.com/2026/05/12/trump-xi-china-summit-rare-earth-trade-critical-minerals/\"},{\"title\":\"White House touts deals on soybeans and rare earths after Trump-Xi summit, while China talks up tariff cuts\",\"url\":\"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/05/18/us-china-announce-deals-after-trump-xi-summit.html\"},{\"title\":\"The aftermath of Trump-Xi summit: comparing U.S. and China announcements : NPR\",\"url\":\"https://www.npr.org/2026/05/22/g-s1-123647/comparing-u-s-and-china-announcements\"},{\"title\":\"Fact Sheet: President Donald J. Trump Secures Historic Deals with China, Delivering for American Workers, Farmers, and Industry – The White House\",\"url\":\"https://www.whitehouse.gov/fact-sheets/2026/05/fact-sheet-president-donald-j-trump-secures-historic-deals-with-china-delivering-for-american-workers-farmers-and-industry/\"},{\"title\":\"Trump, Xi meeting could shape rare earths deal - E&E News by POLITICO\",\"url\":\"https://www.eenews.net/articles/trump-xi-meeting-could-shape-rare-earths-deal/\"},{\"title\":\"Trump-Xi Meeting to Focus on Trade, Rare Earths, and AI\",\"url\":\"https://foreignpolicy.com/2026/05/13/trump-china-xi-jinping-summit-trade-rare-earths-artificial-intelligence/\"},{\"title\":\"FACTBOX: Trump-Xi summit to tackle China's rare earth dominance | S&P Global\",\"url\":\"https://www.spglobal.com/energy/en/news-research/latest-news/metals/051326-factbox-trump-xi-summit-to-tackle-chinas-rare-earth-dominance\"},{\"title\":\"Critical Minerals, Lasting Trade Deal Key to Meaningful Trump-Xi Summit - Information Technology Industry Council\",\"url\":\"https://www.itic.org/news-events/techwonk-blog/critical-minerals-lasting-trade-deal-key-to-meaningful-trumpxi-summit\"},{\"title\":\"Xi warns Trump: Mishandling Taiwan will put U.S.-China relationship in 'great jeopardy'\",\"url\":\"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/05/14/trump-xi-beijing-summit-trade-taiwan-ai-iran-rare-earths-tariffs.html\"}]\n\nBased on the search results, I found information about the Trump-Xi summit and rare earth trade dealings in May 2026:\n\n## Summit Date and Location\n\nThe Trump-Xi summit took place in Beijing on May 14-15, 2026, with Trump and Xi meeting on May 15 at final talks of the superpower summit.\n\n## Rare Earths Trade Deal\n\nChina agreed to address U.S. concerns regarding supply chain shortages related to rare earths and other critical minerals, including yttrium, scandium, neodymium, and indium, as well as prohibitions or restrictions on the sale of rare earth production and processing equipment and technologies.\n\nHowever, there were some differences in how the two sides characterized the agreement. The United States stated that China would address U.S. concerns on mineral supply shortages and sales restrictions on rare earth production and processing equipment and technologies, while China maintained that its export controls on rare earths and other critical minerals are lawful, and said it reviews applications that are compliant and for civilian use.\n\n## Additional Agreements\n\nBeyond rare earths, China approved an initial purchase of 200 American-made Boeing aircraft for Chinese airlines, and China agreed to purchase at least $17 billion per year of U.S. agricultural products in 2026 (prorated), 2027, and 2028.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_018dZEMFFbxCBMwW5jUrv2aX","session_id":"fe1a4df5-a4ab-4fab-90bd-ba1de175a1ca","uuid":"36a4c626-21cc-4a74-8723-9209d4a1588a","timestamp":"2026-05-31T23:02:58.738Z","subagent_type":"general-purpose","task_description":"Equities & sectors researc