{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01V4MxFNJoL55KDeQk9wjd3G","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"\"May 29 2026\" OR \"May 2026\" market breadth advance decline new highs S&P 500 record\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Advance / Decline Line for S&P 500, Dow, Nasdaq - MarketInOut.com\",\"url\":\"https://www.marketinout.com/chart/market.php?breadth=advance-decline-line\"},{\"title\":\"Smarter Stock Market Charts & Tools for Investors | StreetStats\",\"url\":\"https://streetstats.finance/\"},{\"title\":\"Stock Market Breadth & Momentum - S&P 500\",\"url\":\"https://streetstats.finance/markets/breadth-momentum/SP500\"},{\"title\":\"May 2026 Market Commentary | Clearview WS\",\"url\":\"https://www.clearviewws.com/may-2026-market-commentary/\"},{\"title\":\"235 New Lows vs 120 New Highs Is the Real Story | TheStreet Pro\",\"url\":\"https://pro.thestreet.com/market-commentary/235-new-lows-vs-120-new-highs-is-the-real-story\"},{\"title\":\"S&P 500 Breadth | UGC Collections\",\"url\":\"https://en.macromicro.me/collections/16106/20Charts_344136/81081/S-P-500-Breadth\"},{\"title\":\"US - S&P 500 Advancers vs. Decliners | US Stock Market | Collection | MacroMicro\",\"url\":\"https://en.macromicro.me/collections/34/us-stock-relative/136200/us-s-p-500-advancers-and-decliners\"},{\"title\":\"Market Breadth Fears Are Everywhere, But Data Tells a More Nuanced Story\",\"url\":\"https://articles.stockcharts.com/article/market-breadth-fears-are-everywhere-but-data-tells-a-more-nuanced-story/\"},{\"title\":\"May 2026 Economic and Market Update: New Highs and Old Risks - Crestwood Advisors\",\"url\":\"https://www.crestwoodadvisors.com/may-2026-economic-and-market-update/\"}]\n\nBased on the search results, here's what I found regarding May 29, 2026 market breadth and S&P 500 conditions:\n\n## S&P 500 Market Levels as of May 29, 2026\n\nAs of market close on May 29, 2026, the S&P 500 was trading at 7580.06, well above its 50-day moving average of 7058.17 and its 200-day moving average of 6830.83. Over the past three months the index tumbled from the high 6800s in early March to a low near 6343.73 in late March before mounting a powerful rebound that carried it back through its February highs and to fresh record levels.\n\n## Market Breadth Indicators\n\nThe breadth picture shows mixed participation. Constituents trading above their 50-day average account for 54.4% of the index, with an index percentile value of 39, pointing to moderate participation in the short-term uptrend. Constituents trading above their 200-day average represent 59%, with an index percentile value of 39, indicating that just under three-fifths of names are in longer-term uptrends.\n\n## Technical Momentum\n\nThe Relative Strength Index (RSI) stands at 73.6, reflecting strong upside momentum and exceeding commonly cited overbought thresholds around 70.\n\n## Overall Assessment\n\nThe market's recent surge has been fueled by exceptional corporate earnings and easing geopolitical tensions, yet key breadth measures point to uneven participation. With fewer than three-fifths of constituents above their key moving averages and only modest fresh highs, broader engagement may be needed to sustain further upward momentum amid lingering inflation pressures and lofty valuations.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_018dZEMFFbxCBMwW5jUrv2aX","session_id":"fe1a4df5-a4ab-4fab-90bd-ba1de175a1ca","uuid":"e483845e-ae7a-40d3-9be9-b2e5f4674881","timestamp":"2026-05-31T23:03:01.804Z","subagent_type":"general-purpose","task_description":"Equities & sectors research"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01RoZUfMiHcymPxeZWmMMRx6","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"Bitcoin price Sunday May 31 2026 BTC dominance current\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"AI model sets Bitcoin price target for May 31, 2026\",\"url\":\"https://cryptonews.net/news/bitcoin/32794481/\"},{\"title\":\"Bitcoin price history May 27, 2026| Statista\",\"url\":\"https://www.statista.com/statistics/326707/bitcoin-price-index/\"},{\"title\":\"Bitcoin Dominance Up or Down Monthly Predictions & Odds 2026 | Polymarket\",\"url\":\"https://polymarket.com/event/bitcoin-dominance-up-or-down-in-may\"},{\"title\":\"Bitcoin Price Perspectives in May 2026\",\"url\":\"https://bitcoinfoundation.org/news/prediction-markets/bitcoin-price-prediction-in-may-2026/\"},{\"title\":\"Bitcoin (BTC) Price Prediction 2026, 2027-2030 | CoinCodex\",\"url\":\"https://coincodex.com/crypto/bitcoin/price-prediction/\"},{\"title\":\"Bitcoin Price Prediction 2026-2031: Can BTC Reclaim $81K?\",\"url\":\"https://coindcx.com/blog/price-predictions/bitcoin-price-weekly/\"},{\"title\":\"Bitcoin (BTC) Price Prediction & Forecast 2026, 2027, 2028-2030 | Binance\",\"url\":\"https://www.binance.com/en/price-prediction/bitcoin\"},{\"title\":\"Bitcoin above ___ on May 31? Trading Odds & Predictions 2026 | Polymarket\",\"url\":\"https://polymarket.com/event/bitcoin-above-on-may-31-2026\"},{\"title\":\"Bitcoin Dominance May 2026: Currently at 57.3% | BTC.D Guide - TradingView Hub\",\"url\":\"https://www.tv-hub.org/guide/bitcoin-dominance\"},{\"title\":\"Bitcoin price prediction 2026-2032: Will BTC hit $150k soon?\",\"url\":\"https://www.cryptopolitan.com/bitcoin-price-prediction/\"}]\n\nBased on the search results, here's what I found about Bitcoin price and dominance information for May 31, 2026:\n\n## Bitcoin Price on May 31, 2026\n\nThe Bitcoin (BTC) price reached an all-time high in 2025, as values exceeded over 75,824.06 USD on May 27, 2026. More recent analysis shows BTC was trading at $73,856, surging by over 0.5% in the last 24 hours.\n\nPrice predictions for May 31 varied among analysts. Finbold's AI price models projected that the flagship cryptocurrency could trade at $76,199 by May 31, 2026. Additionally, the price of Bitcoin was predicted to increase by 5%-8% and may reach $76,000-$82,000 by the end of May 2026.\n\n## Bitcoin Dominance\n\nRegarding Bitcoin dominance, Bitcoin Dominance (BTC.D) is 57.3% in May 2026. However, by May, some figures hovered close to 58.91%, while certain trackers recorded values slightly over 61%.\n\nBitcoin's market dominance edged higher to 60.16%, according to market data. A rise in dominance often signals that capital is rotating away from altcoins and back into Bitcoin.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01PHSkBGNFVsYNfGY6YDTHaK","session_id":"fe1a4df5-a4ab-4fab-90bd-ba1de175a1ca","uuid":"d56a67ce-bd9b-4d0f-b299-9536167364c5","timestamp":"2026-05-31T23:03:04.170Z","subagent_type":"general-purpose","task_description":"Crypto & alternative research"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_015NUKSBVisZKV4ePeb96MJW","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"bitcoin price May 30 31 2026 weekend\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Bitcoin Price on May 30: Will BTC Land in the $76K-$78K Band?\",\"url\":\"https://www.lines.com/prediction-markets/crypto/bitcoin-price-on-may-30-2026\"},{\"title\":\"Bitcoin price history May 27, 2026| Statista\",\"url\":\"https://www.statista.com/statistics/326707/bitcoin-price-index/\"},{\"title\":\"Bitcoin Price (Daily) - Historical Data & Trends\",\"url\":\"https://ycharts.com/indicators/bitcoin_price\"},{\"title\":\"Bitcoin USD (BTC-USD) Price History & Historical Data - Yahoo Finance\",\"url\":\"https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/BTC-USD/history/\"},{\"title\":\"Current price of Bitcoin for May 29, 2026 | Fortune\",\"url\":\"https://fortune.com/article/price-of-bitcoin-05-29-2026/\"},{\"title\":\"Bitcoin Price Prediction, Short/Long Forecast - CoinLore\",\"url\":\"https://www.coinlore.com/coin/bitcoin/forecast/price-prediction\"},{\"title\":\"Bitcoin (BTC) Price USD Today, News, Charts, Market Cap | Coinbase\",\"url\":\"https://www.coinbase.com/price/bitcoin\"},{\"title\":\"Machine learning algorithm predicts Bitcoin price for May 31, 2026\",\"url\":\"https://finbold.com/machine-learning-algorithm-predicts-bitcoin-price-for-may-31-2026/\"},{\"title\":\"Machine learning algorithm predicts Bitcoin price for May 31, 2026\",\"url\":\"https://cryptonews.net/news/bitcoin/32849723/\"},{\"title\":\"BTC price range on May 30, 2026 at 11am EDT Prediction Market\",\"url\":\"https://robinhood.com/us/en/prediction-markets/crypto/events/btc-price-range-on-may-30-2026-at-11am-edt-may-29-2026/\"}]\n\nBased on the search results, here's what I found regarding Bitcoin prices for the weekend of May 30-31, 2026:\n\n## Current Prices\n\nBitcoin was trading at 73,751.07 USD on May 31, 2026, while the price was at $73,413.04 on the same day (with slight variations depending on the source and exact time).\n\n## May 30 Price Range\n\nBitcoin reached an all-time high in 2025, with values exceeding over 75,824.06 USD on May 27, 2026. However, the price declined toward the weekend.\n\n## Predictions and Technical Analysis\n\nThere were various predictions made for May 31:\n- Finbold AI expected BTC price to close May trading at $79,325, down nearly 2% from May 12\n- Over the next 24 hours, BTC was predicted to trade between $72,289 and $75,523\n\n## Weekend Market Context\n\nThe weekend saw mixed market sentiment, with bitcoin and ether ETFs losing roughly $2 billion combined from May 20 to May 29, indicating some broader weakness in the crypto market during this period.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01Q8Kwt517HqYVMRhJgQ1kZ1","session_id":"fe1a4df5-a4ab-4fab-90bd-ba1de175a1ca","uuid":"bcaa9df2-2280-46de-8c4f-6986681185e0","timestamp":"2026-05-31T23:03:04.281Z","subagent_type":"general-purpose","task_description":"Commodities & forex research"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_019NaPVCEYQgod9oj5AndE2R","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"gold price weekly change May 2026 record high monthly Iran war safe haven\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"How US-Iran War Affects Gold Price: Safe Haven Rush ...\",\"url\":\"https://intellectia.ai/blog/us-iran-war-affect-gold-price-2026-analysis\"},{\"title\":\"Gold and silver prices plunge: Why has safe-haven demand faded amid Iran war? | Euronews\",\"url\":\"https://www.euronews.com/business/2026/03/30/gold-and-silver-prices-plunge-why-has-safe-haven-demand-faded-amid-iran-war\"},{\"title\":\"Gold heads for weekly gain as hopes for US-Iran deal ease inflation fears | Kitco News\",\"url\":\"https://www.kitco.com/news/off-the-wire/2026-05-08/gold-heads-weekly-gain-hopes-us-iran-deal-ease-inflation-fears\"},{\"title\":\"Gold - Price - Chart - Historical Data - News\",\"url\":\"https://tradingeconomics.com/commodity/gold\"},{\"title\":\"US-Iran War Gold Price Impact: What Investors Need to Know\",\"url\":\"https://discoveryalert.com.au/gold-response-middle-eastern-geopolitical-conflicts-2026/\"}]\n\nBased on the search results, here's information about gold price movements in May 2026 related to the Iran war and safe-haven demand:\n\n## Weekly Performance in May 2026\n\nAs of May 8, bullion had gained 2.3% for the week as markets priced in optimism over a prospective U.S.–Iran peace agreement.\n\n## Record Highs and Monthly Performance\n\nGold hit an all-time high of $5,602 (€4,873) at the end of January. However, by late May, prices were on track for a 0.8% monthly decline, pressured by inflation concerns and expectations of prolonged higher interest rates.\n\n## Safe-Haven Impact During the War\n\nThe escalating conflict between the United States, Israel, and Iran triggered a historic surge in gold prices, with spot gold blasting past $5,300 per ounce for the first time in history. The immediate catalyst came on February 28, 2026, when coordinated US and Israeli strikes on Iranian targets triggered panic buying, with gold futures surging over 2% in a single session, pushing prices from approximately $5,100 to over $5,300 per ounce.\n\nHowever, gold had fallen more than 10% since the war began in late February, pressured by higher oil prices that have stoked inflation concerns, showing that despite initial safe-haven demand, other economic factors have weighed on prices.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01Q8Kwt517HqYVMRhJgQ1kZ1","session_id":"fe1a4df5-a4ab-4fab-90bd-ba1de175a1ca","uuid":"44c6c871-725f-4091-b16a-9355d1cdb6e2","timestamp":"2026-05-31T23:03:04.861Z","subagent_type":"general-purpose","task_description":"Commodities & forex research"}
