{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01GoxspzmYfRwRQ36eLCvRxK","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"Sunday May 31 2026 markets news OpenAI Anthropic deal merger acquisition announcement\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"The Trillion-Dollar IPO Test: SpaceX and OpenAI Face Public Markets | Investing.com\",\"url\":\"https://www.investing.com/analysis/the-trilliondollar-ipo-test-spacex-and-openai-face-public-markets-200680688\"},{\"title\":\"SpaceX, OpenAI, Anthropic: upcoming IPOs to watch in 2026 | IG International\",\"url\":\"https://www.ig.com/en/news-and-trade-ideas/spacex-openai-anthropic-2026-ipo-deals-260520\"},{\"title\":\"My guide to the IPOs of SpaceX, OpenAI and Anthropic — including the one I really want to buy\",\"url\":\"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/05/31/my-guide-to-the-ipos-of-spacex-openai-and-anthropic-including-the-one-i-really-want-to-buy.html\"},{\"title\":\"SpaceX, OpenAI & Anthropic IPOs 2026 | Dates, Valuations, Risks & Market Impact\",\"url\":\"https://www.indmoney.com/blog/us-stocks/spacex-openai-anthropic-ipo-explained\"},{\"title\":\"Anthropic tops OpenAI as most valuable AI startup, nears $1 trillion valuation in latest round\",\"url\":\"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/05/28/anthropic-open-ai-startup-value.html\"},{\"title\":\"SpaceX, OpenAI, and Anthropic in IPO Race for AI Boom\",\"url\":\"https://thehill.com/policy/technology/5892110-openai-spacex-anthropic-stock-market/\"},{\"title\":\"Anthropic and OpenAI are both launching joint ventures for enterprise AI services | TechCrunch\",\"url\":\"https://techcrunch.com/2026/05/04/anthropic-and-openai-are-both-launching-joint-ventures-for-enterprise-ai-services/\"}]\n\nBased on the search results, I found information about market news from around May 31, 2026, but I did not find any announcement of a deal, merger, or acquisition between OpenAI and Anthropic.\n\nHere's what was actually happening in the markets on that date:\n\n**IPO Pipeline News:**\nElon Musk's SpaceX is in pole position and is supposed to debut within two weeks (as of May 31). Only SpaceX has officially released its initial public offering prospectus known as an S-1, while CNBC reported OpenAI is working on a confidential filing, and others suggest Anthropic could come public as soon as the fourth quarter.\n\n**Anthropic's Recent Fundraising:**\nAnthropic announced a $65 billion Series H financing at a $965 billion valuation, a round led by Altimeter Capital, Dragoneer, Greenoaks and Sequoia Capital. The financing puts its valuation above that of rival AI lab OpenAI. Anthropic reported a $47 billion revenue run rate, up from a $30 billion run rate earlier this year, and $10 billion in annual revenue last year.\n\n**Market Context:**\nRather than a merger or acquisition between the two companies, the news centered on their separate paths to going public and their competitive positioning in the AI market.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_018dZEMFFbxCBMwW5jUrv2aX","session_id":"fe1a4df5-a4ab-4fab-90bd-ba1de175a1ca","uuid":"9b72f804-9627-49d5-a095-9f19c35a57d0","timestamp":"2026-05-31T23:03:13.469Z","subagent_type":"general-purpose","task_description":"Equities & sectors research"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_018VQt98NLTgT6butoEVypex","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"AMD Marvell Micron TSMC semiconductor stocks week ending May 29 2026\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Taiwan Semiconductor Manufacturing Company Limited (TSM) Stock Price, News, Quote & History - Yahoo Finance\",\"url\":\"https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/TSM/\"},{\"title\":\"Why Marvell Technology (MRVL) Shares Are Sliding Today\",\"url\":\"https://finance.yahoo.com/markets/stocks/articles/why-marvell-technology-mrvl-shares-165255576.html\"},{\"title\":\"Advanced Micro Devices, Inc. (AMD) Stock Price, News, Quote & History - Yahoo Finance\",\"url\":\"https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/AMD/\"},{\"title\":\"Cathie Wood dumps more semiconductor stocks in blindsiding move\",\"url\":\"https://www.thestreet.com/investing/stocks/cathie-wood-dumps-28m-of-amd-and-tsm-in-surprise-move\"},{\"title\":\"Why Marvell Technology (MRVL) Shares Are Sliding Today - StockStory\",\"url\":\"https://stockstory.org/us/stocks/nasdaq/mrvl/news/why-up-down/why-marvell-technology-mrvl-shares-are-sliding-today-2\"},{\"title\":\"Top Semiconductor Stocks for 2026: AMD, AVGO, MU, MRVL, and ADI\",\"url\":\"https://www.marketbeat.com/stock-ideas/beyond-nvidia-5-semiconductor-stocks-set-to-dominate-2026/\"},{\"title\":\"Top Semiconductor Stocks Investors Are Watching in May: Nvida, AMD, Micron Lead - CoinCentral\",\"url\":\"https://coincentral.com/top-semiconductor-stocks-investors-are-watching-in-may-nvida-amd-micron-lead/\"},{\"title\":\"FinancialContent - Why Marvell Technology (MRVL) Shares Are Sliding Today\",\"url\":\"https://markets.financialcontent.com/stocks/article/stockstory-2026-5-18-why-marvell-technology-mrvl-shares-are-sliding-today\"},{\"title\":\"Could These Be the Smartest Stocks to Buy After Taking Profits on AMD and Micron? | The Motley Fool\",\"url\":\"https://www.fool.com/investing/2026/05/29/could-these-be-the-smartest-stocks-to-buy-after-ta/\"},{\"title\":\"AMD Stock Quote Price and Forecast | CNN\",\"url\":\"https://www.cnn.com/markets/stocks/AMD\"}]\n\nBased on the search results for semiconductor stocks during the week ending May 29, 2026, here's what I found:\n\n## Stock Performance Overview\n\n**AMD**: AMD closed around $422 and was up roughly 98% year-to-date as of late May. AMD reported a 37.9% year-over-year revenue increase, with data-center revenue up 57%.\n\n**Marvell Technology**: Marvell is up 86.9% since the beginning of the year, and at $167.11 per share, it is trading close to its 52-week high of $182.58 from May 2026.\n\n**TSMC**: Taiwan Semiconductor Manufacturing Company has experienced a 5% increase in stock price over the past month and a notable 31% year-to-date rise, with current shares valued at $418.45.\n\n**Micron**: Micron had its best week since 2008, rising 30% over five sessions on AI memory demand.\n\n## Market Sentiment\n\nThe semiconductor sector faced headwinds during this period. Shares of Marvell fell 5.3% in the afternoon session after a broad-based sell-off hit the semiconductor sector following news of a potential strike at Samsung and a stake sale by Taiwan Semiconductor Manufacturing, which highlighted significant supply-chain risks. Rising valuation concerns, inflation fears, and ongoing supply constraints for rare earth materials compounded negative sentiment for chip-related stocks.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_018dZEMFFbxCBMwW5jUrv2aX","session_id":"fe1a4df5-a4ab-4fab-90bd-ba1de175a1ca","uuid":"d9cbb5a9-b453-4ce9-80b4-394dd862a6c9","timestamp":"2026-05-31T23:03:13.638Z","subagent_type":"general-purpose","task_description":"Equities & sectors research"}
